{"type": "article", "id": 5340, "title": "A Table 系列餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-19T07:57:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233726VZrRYM6Tmab5hjWH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#292929;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t意大利贝纳通集团旗下 Fabrica 工作室日前为意大利设计品牌 Atipico 带来最新的餐具系列「A Table」，将亮相于本周开幕的巴黎家具装饰博览会。 Fabrica 意图借由这套餐具表达出当代用餐空间跨民族、跨国家之间的餐饮文化的融合，包括碗、玻璃水瓶、碟子、勺子以及砧板等，选用了陶瓷、织物、玻璃、金属和木材等不同的物料进行制造。其中不少细节颇有趣味，比如小型砧板可以作为碗的盖子，勺子的中间做成了轻微折痕状，提供了更好的抓附力。而杯子的轮廓则受到了日本茶道文化中所用杯形的影响。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#292929;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233723aJvl54mMSkZrAW37.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233723iLqzOBGYa8p47XNP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233724jglL0GF67sbC1QOq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233724xrWS2dYsygfRXVNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233725BE0rYtcFDsIPkVLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233725boQY2TSRGzPE8ODk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}